title: Stop Rewarding Yourself With Food
itunes:title: Stop Rewarding Yourself With Food
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

"I like to reward myself with food. Is that okay?" The answer is NO. In this podcast I teach you why this sets you up for diet disaster. I give you some ideas on better rewards one of which is just learning how to take pride in a job well done!
